What is ansible facts: 
======================
Ansible facts are nothing but information about managed nodes like: os, distrubution,
release, processor, python, etc....!!!

This task of collecting this remote system i
nformation is called as Gathering facts , Gatherd 
informatio is called facts or Variables.

We can gather/Collect facts using setup module in Ad-hoc commands`

Note: 
====
Ansible playbooks call this setup module by DEFAULT to perform Gathering Facts task. 


We can display ansible facts using setup module using ansible ad-hoc command
# ansible web -m setup 